  "root_text": {
    "an10.80:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10.80 ",
    "an10.80:0.2": "8. Ākaṅkhavagga ",
    "an10.80:0.3": "Āghātapaṭivinayasutta ",
    "an10.80:1.1": "“Dasayime, bhikkhave, āghātapaṭivinayā. ",
    "an10.80:1.2": "Katame dasa? ",
    "an10.80:1.3": "‘Anatthaṁ me acari, taṁ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṁ paṭivineti, ",
    "an10.80:1.4": "‘anatthaṁ me carati, taṁ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṁ paṭivineti, ",
    "an10.80:1.5": "‘anatthaṁ me carissati, taṁ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṁ paṭivineti, ",
    "an10.80:1.6": "piyassa me manāpassa anatthaṁ acari …pe… ",
    "an10.80:1.7": "carati …pe… ",
    "an10.80:1.8": "carissati, taṁ kutettha labbhāti āghātaṁ paṭivineti, appiyassa me amanāpassa atthaṁ acari …pe… ",
    "an10.80:1.9": "atthaṁ carati …pe… ",
    "an10.80:1.10": "atthaṁ carissati, taṁ kutettha labbhāti āghātaṁ paṭivineti, ",
    "an10.80:1.11": "aṭṭhāne ca na kuppati—",
    "an10.80:1.12": "ime kho, bhikkhave, dasa āghātapaṭivinayā”ti. ",
    "an10.80:1.13": "Dasamaṁ. ",
    "an10.80:1.14": "Ākaṅkhavaggo tatiyo. ",
    "an10.80:2.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
    "an10.80:2.1": "Ākaṅkho kaṇṭako iṭṭhā, ",
    "an10.80:2.2": "vaḍḍhi ca migasālāya; ",
    "an10.80:2.3": "Tayo dhammā ca kāko ca, ",
    "an10.80:2.4": "nigaṇṭhā dve ca āghātāti. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "an10.80:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 10.80 ",
    "an10.80:0.2": "8. If You Want ",
    "an10.80:0.3": "Getting Rid of Resentment ",
    "an10.80:1.1": "“Mendicants, there are these ten ways to get rid of resentment. ",
    "an10.80:1.2": "What ten? ",
    "an10.80:1.3": "Thinking: ‘They harmed me, but what can I possibly do?’ you get rid of resentment. ",
    "an10.80:1.4": "Thinking: ‘They are harming me …’ … ",
    "an10.80:1.5": "‘They will harm me …’ … ",
    "an10.80:1.6": "‘They harmed someone I love …’ … ",
    "an10.80:1.7": "‘They are harming someone I love …’ ",
    "an10.80:1.8": "‘They will harm someone I love …’ … They helped someone I dislike …’ … ",
    "an10.80:1.9": "‘They are helping someone I dislike …’ … ",
    "an10.80:1.10": "Thinking: ‘They will help someone I dislike, but what can I possibly do?’ you get rid of resentment. ",
    "an10.80:1.11": "And you don’t get angry for no reason. ",
    "an10.80:1.12": "These are the ten ways of getting rid of resentment.” ",
